      "content": "i just feel like you're being super strict about it. i've heard people do this all the time and they're fine. if i just have like a few sips, it would basically just act like a booster for the diazepam right? it would help me relax way faster than just the pill alone. if i'm careful, isn't it basically just helping the process?",
